===Pronunciation===

===Noun===

1.  The governing council of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union and other Leninist political systems.

2.  (Informal):  a senior policymaking body in a political organisation, generally consisting of members who either are appointed by the party in control of the organisation or who attain membership through their personal political affiliations.  This form is often used to cast doubt on the legitimacy or stated goals of the subject.

